  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t知乎这个回答下，一位答主发了两个视频：<br/>\r\n人麻了<br/>\r\n一个是一位男学生一边在食堂拼命狼吞虎咽，一边看秒表，生怕超过吃饭还回教室的时限。另一个是一位教师查谁在上课说话，如同审讯犯人。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n评论区一片痛斥，许多人回忆自己的中学经历，也都愤怒不已。显然大多数国人已经明白“衡水模式”不是好东西，比前些年吹捧“衡水模式”可以“寒门出贵子”强多了。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n但是，无人以行动反抗、无人走上街头、无人挥黄钺。<br/>\n<br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvYmZkN2YzN2JkZDE0OThjMTkxZjVkLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/bfd7f37bdd1498c191f5d.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/bfd7f37bdd1498c191f5d.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/bfd7f37bdd1498c191f5d.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMDgwNjFiYjU4YjRlZGFkMjE4MWMyLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/08061bb58b4edad2181c2.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/08061bb58b4edad2181c2.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/08061bb58b4edad2181c2.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvODM1ZTJiOWY5MDZiMjYzY2E5YWE2LnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/835e2b9f906b263ca9aa6.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/835e2b9f906b263ca9aa6.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/835e2b9f906b263ca9aa6.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvMDExYjU4MGYyYjA5MGFmNGVkMmNhLnBuZw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://telegra.ph/file/011b580f2b090af4ed2ca.png\"><img alt=\"https://telegra.ph/file/011b580f2b090af4ed2ca.png\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://telegra.ph/file/011b580f2b090af4ed2ca.png\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a><a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvOTY5Mzc0MjIzMDJkZWMwOGU0Mjc0LnBuZw\" rel